{"tid":1959300,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙格拿：雲加離開後阿仙奴變成了馬戲團","createTime":"2020-04-05T09:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T15:04:17.000Z","uid":165817,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3095e2c29e40bef57eac0ff7a11a424e5c688e","tid":1959300,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"前阿仙奴後衛沙格拿早前在專訪中將阿仙奴稱為「馬戲團」，在球迷圈子引起話題。沙格拿近日直接表示，他所指的馬戲團，就是阿仙奴的管理層。<br />\n<br />\n沙格拿說：「當你管有一間悠久的球會的時候，你怎可以碌碌無為？我希望看到球會的野心，並不是一定是要花很多錢，但至少需要有人正確地管理球會。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不知道現在是誰在做重大的決定。在過去，你知道是由雲加來做決定的，他是領導者，但自從他離開後，我不知道阿仙奴是由誰在領導。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，像阿仙奴這樣的球會需要更多的領導力，因此我才會說他如今更像是一個馬戲團。」<br />\n<br />\n「阿仙奴高層根本就沒有為球會作出一個長期的規劃，令現在的阿仙奴已經落後於其他球隊。」"},{"pid":"687d339bfaeb79568ebc2d6610932a8f2be8b3bc","tid":1959300,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"fcd6fbc39f2495189776da12e5e293f1884b84bf","tid":1959300,"uid":39812,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/VastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FVastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif&h=7a584c55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d832f3130fdc8936cd0210a298d874cf7d45705e","tid":1959300,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:59:34.000Z","msg":"他所指的馬戲團，就是阿仙奴的管理層。"},{"pid":"58d0473d9e06e9cd8918b9f009178433837ed487","tid":1959300,"uid":165817,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fcd6fbc39f2495189776da12e5e293f1884b84bf","tid":1959300,"uid":39812,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/VastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FVastTatteredGrasshopper-max-1mb.gif&h=7a584c55&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20